---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Quality Control - Weiyijie Bio">
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Quality Control System</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We have a strict 4-step quality control process to ensure every batch of products meets your quality requirements and international standards.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- 步骤1：来料检测 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-3xl font-bold mx-auto">1</div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Raw Material Inspection</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">All incoming raw materials are strictly inspected before entering the warehouse:
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
                  <li>Visual inspection of appearance, color, odor and packaging</li>
                  <li>Test of moisture content, purity and active ingredient content</li>
                  <li>Microbial test for bacteria, mold and yeast</li>
                  <li>Heavy metal test for lead, arsenic, mercury and cadmium</li>
                  <li>Pesticide residue test to ensure compliance with international standards</li>
                </ul>
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Only raw materials that pass all tests are allowed to enter the production process. Unqualified raw materials are returned directly to suppliers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 步骤2：生产过程检测 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-3xl font-bold mx-auto">2</div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">In-Process Quality Control</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We conduct real-time monitoring and testing during the entire production process:
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
                  <li>Monitoring of extraction temperature, pressure and time parameters</li>
                  <li>Regular sampling and testing of semi-finished products</li>
                  <li>Control of purification, concentration and drying processes</li>
                  <li>Real-time adjustment of process parameters to ensure product consistency</li>
                  <li>Strict hygiene management of production environment and equipment</li>
                </ul>
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Our quality control team inspects every production stage to ensure that all process parameters meet the specified standards before proceeding to the next stage.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 步骤3：成品检测 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-3xl font-bold mx-auto">3</div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Finished Product Testing</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Every batch of finished products undergoes comprehensive testing before leaving the factory:
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
                  <li>Full test of appearance, solubility, particle size and color</li>
                  <li>Precise test of active ingredient content using HPLC/GC/UV spectrophotometer</li>
                  <li>Microbial limit test (total plate count, coliform, yeast, mold, pathogenic bacteria)</li>
                  <li>Heavy metal and pesticide residue test</li>
                  <li>Stability test under different temperature and humidity conditions</li>
                  <li>Packaging inspection to ensure no damage and proper labeling</li>
                </ul>
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Only products that pass all tests are allowed to be shipped. Each batch of products comes with a complete Certificate of Analysis (COA) with all test results.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 步骤4：留样追溯 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-3xl font-bold mx-auto">4</div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Sample Retention & Traceability System</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We have a complete sample retention and traceability system for every batch of products:
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
                  <li>Each batch of products is retained for at least 2 years after the shelf life</li>
                  <li>Complete production records are kept for each batch, including raw material sources, production parameters and test results</li>
                  <li>All products can be traced back to the original raw material batch and production date</li>
                  <li>We can provide full traceability documents upon request</li>
                </ul>
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">This system ensures that we can quickly investigate and resolve any quality issues that may arise after delivery, and continuously improve our production process.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Want to learn more about our quality control process or request COA samples? Contact our team today.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all">
          Request COA Sample
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
